name: Overbooked (Vitbull88, carrapaz, lbere, KrustyTincan)
description:
Your connecting flight is departing! 

Hurry up, don't miss it! Grab your luggage, check it in, pass through security, and find your gate before the plane departs. But, it won't be that easy....

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Gameplay Instructions:

Walk using the WASD keys

Sprint using the SHIFT key

Launch the trolley using the left mouse button or spacebar

Interact with objects using the E key

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Note: player animations sometimes work, sometimes don't. You can try reloading the page (web) or restarting the game (download), if you are lucky animations will play. After the jam we'll try to fix this weird issue, that gave us bad headache. Sorry for the inconvenience. If you experienced anything like this, let us know in the comments thanks!
